22-005SC.summary: Recommendation to approve the minutes of the Sustainable City Commission meeting of Thursday, January 27, 2022.Dave Shukla spoke.A motion was made by Commissioner Skye, seconded by Commissioner Gonzales, to approve recommendation.  The motion carried by the following vote:Yes: 6 - Keisha Gaines, Rey Gonzales, Jenny Novak, Coby Skye, Sona Coffee and Morgan WheelerAbsent: 5 - Donna Bergeron-Birge, Carla Dillon, Eric Rock, Alan Tolkoff and Hilda Gaytan2.
